    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1007192388">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1007192388" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1007192388" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1007192388">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/vedacode/">茄子</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者的分析叙述构成一个独特的场域。虽然儿时生活在农村，但是作者所描述的事件还是让人大开眼界。从理论上来分析其中的机理也让人有很多的启发。只是我还是觉得，对于法理或是公民，无论是哪里都是缺乏的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="596820678">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-596820678" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-596820678" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="596820678">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yvespotter/">Yves Potter</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-10-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">能在娓娓叙说间将那些溶解和渗透于日常生活中的社会机制和博弈逻辑说清楚，足显作者见解深刻、功底扎实。所有被半吊子学术训练毒害太深的僵化头脑，都应该反复阅读本书，暂时忘掉数据库里那几个苍白空洞的变量，悉心体会由结构性因素与能动性因素在特定社会场域中相互作用而构建出的政治过程。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1045388080">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1045388080" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1045388080" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1045388080">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ruomuyu/">若木1.5。</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">2016-25 自《中县干部》的参考文献中来</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="437568696">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-437568696" class="vote-count">1</span>
